            "content_html": "<main>\n    <p>\n\tSummary of BCD changes from <a href=\"\"><time title=\"Monday, 20 April 2026\">Monday, 20 April 2026</time></a> through <time title=\"Monday, 27 April 2026\">Monday, 27 April 2026</time></strong><a href=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/weekly-completed/2026-04-27.html\" title=\"permalink\">🔗</a>\n    </p>\n    <hr>\n\n\n          <p class=\"callout\"><strong>2 new universal implementations</strong></p>\n          <section class=\"added implementations\">\n\t            <h4>API</h4>\n              <ol>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>api ➞ GPURenderBundleEncoder ➞ setVertexBuffer ➞ unset_vertex_buffer\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>api ➞ GPURenderPassEncoder ➞ setVertexBuffer ➞ unset_vertex_buffer\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n              </ol>\n          </section>\n\n  <hr>\n  <ul id=\"prev-next\">\n  \t<li>Previous report: <a href=\"\"><time title=\"Monday, 20 April 2026\">Monday, 20 April 2026</time></a></li>\n  </ul>\n  <hr>\n  <footer>\n  \t<p>\n  \t<a href=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/\">BCD Watch</a>: A service of <a href=\"https://igalia.com\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/igalia-logo.png\" alt=\"Igalia\"></a>\n  \t</p>\n  \t<p>\n  \tSubscribe: <a href=\"feed.rss\">RSS</a> • <a href=\"feed.atom\">A